t: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">নমুন</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;;\">া। </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">বলার</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">অপেক্ষা রাখে\r\nনা, শারীরিক</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">ও</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">মানসিক</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">স্বাস্থ্যের</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">জন্য</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">প্রতিষ্ঠিত</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">পন্থা হলো—কার্যকর</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">চিকিৎস</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;;\">া। </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">শরীরের</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">সুস্থতা,\r\nআত্মার</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">পবিত্রতা, চিন্তার</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">স্বচ্ছতা আর</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">মনের</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">স্নিগ্ধতার</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">পাশাপাশি উন্নত</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"> </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Vrinda, sans-serif;\">বোধ</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">